stylometry: Risk simtable allows you to take more than one input lets say 5 inputs the simtable will then simulate these inputs by processing them through 1000 itterations and coming up with the average mean and standard devation, also with the max and min. Lets say you have a store and you want to know how much product to sell which will be most profitable. The simtable will again take your product quanities run them through 1000 itterations and come up with a chart that will show you which input will provide the best profit. You want the input with the lowest standard deviation and the highest mean.
